      <title>加拿大，墨西哥的关税不受特朗普贸易转变的改变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/canada-mexico-tariffs-are-left-unchanged-by-trump-trade-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位白宫官员说，唐纳德·特朗普总统周三突然改变关税政策不会影响目前适用加拿大和墨西哥产品的利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/canada-mexico-tariffs-are-left-unchanged-by-trump-trade-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 20:00:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
